ww.nbcnews.com/world/europe/leipzig-car-strikes-crowd-injured-germany-rcna343482</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-leipzig-germany-car-drives-into-crowd-mn-1230-1afcbf.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Jan Woitas</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Car driven into group of people in Leipzig</media:text><media:description type="plain">Rescue workers stand near a damaged car at the spot where a car crashed into a group of people in Leipzig, Germany on May 4, 2026. License plate was pixellated by source.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-leipzig-germany-car-drives-into-crowd-mn-1230-1afcbf.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 16:43:43 GMT</pubDate><title>Car runs into crowd in Leipzig, Germany, injuring several people</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 16:43:43 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Corky Siemaszko</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Spirit Airlines said in court papers filed Monday that it was forced to ground its fleet for good over the weekend because &#34;recent geopolitical events resulted in a massive and sustained increase in fuel prices.&#34;While the court papers did not specify the nature of those geopolitical events, jet fuel prices have soared in the two months since the start of the war in Iran.&#34;The Debtors and their advisors searched for increased capital and any sources of savings or liquidity, leaving no option unexp</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/travel/spirit-airlines-doomed-sky-high-fuel-prices-due-recent-geopolitical-ev-rcna343466</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/travel/spirit-airlines-doomed-sky-high-fuel-prices-due-recent-geopolitical-ev-rcna343466</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-spirit-airlines-ew-1126a-8debc2.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Giorgio Viera</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Spirit Airlines</media:text><media:description type="plain">Spirit Airlines jets sit on the tarmac as the company ceased operations at Fort Lauderdale-Hollywood International Airport in Fort Lauderdale, Fla., on May 2, 2026. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-spirit-airlines-ew-1126a-8debc2.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</pubDate><title>Spirit Airlines doomed by high fuel prices due to &#39;recent geopolitical events,&#39; court docs state</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:53:56 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The red carpet at the 2026 Met Gala is just hours away where the red carpet is set to be filled with some of the biggest names in Hollywood, business and pop culture including the long-awaited return of Beyoncé. This year’s theme is a nod to the costume institute’s newest exhibit titled “Costume Art,” but the event is also drawing controversy after it was announced that Amazon founder Jeff Bezos and his wife Lauren Sanchez Bezos would serve as lead sponsors of the event as well as honor</description><expires>2056-05-04T13:53:01.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_8a_jones_met_gala_preview_260504</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/what-to-expect-from-2026-met-gala-dress-code-beyonce-more-262651461810</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_8a_jones_met_gala_preview_260504/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>All on Eyes on 2026 Met Gala: Here&#39;s What to Expect</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/what-to-expect-from-2026-met-gala-dress-code-beyonce-more-262651461810"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/beyonce-met-t8f2em.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The red carpet at the 2026 Met Gala is just hours away where the red carpet is set to be filled with some of the biggest names in Hollywood, business and pop culture including the long-awaited return of Beyoncé. This year’s theme is a nod to the costume institute’s newest exhibit titled “Costume Art,” but the event is also drawing controversy after it was announced that Amazon founder Jeff Bezos and his wife Lauren Sanchez Bezos would serve as lead sponsors of the event as well as honorary co-chairs. TODAY’s Sheinelle Jones shares what to expect from fashion’s biggest night.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/tdy_news_8a_jones_met_gala_preview_260504_0947.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/tdy_news_8a_jones_met_gala_preview_260504_0947.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/beyonce-met-t8f2em.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:49:32 GMT</pubDate><title>All on Eyes on 2026 Met Gala: Here&#39;s What to Expect</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:53:56 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:24:31 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Supreme Court temporarily restores access to abortion pill</description><expires>2056-05-04T17:23:42.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">f_vert_brk_scotus_mife_260504</guid><link>https://www.nbc